  "content": "<div><br></div>\n<div><font face=\".AppleColorEmojiUI\">📆</font> 3. Weekly XP &amp Party-Based System</div>\n<div><br></div>\n<div><font face=\".AppleColorEmojiUI\">📜</font> Students can form “parties” (small groups) to gain collective XP.</div>\n<div><font face=\"ZapfDingbatsITC\">✔</font> If the entire class submits an assignment on time, they unlock a class-wide bonus.</div>\n<div><font face=\"ZapfDingbatsITC\">✔</font> If a party of three submits perfect work, they gain a temporary boost (deadline extension, extra XP, etc.).</div>\n<div><font face=\"ZapfDingbatsITC\">✔</font> If a student completes all assignments in a category (Creative, Discussions, Close Readings), they unlock a title or badge.</div>\n<div><br></div>\n<div>XP &amp Unlockable Perks</div>\n<div><br></div>\n<div><object><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; direction: ltr\">\n<tbody>\n<tr><td valign=\"top\" style=\"border-style: solid; border-width: 1.0px 1.0px 1.0px 1.0px; border-color: #ccc; padding: 3.0px 5.0px 3.0px 5.0px; min-width: 70px\"><div>XP Achievement</div>\n</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"border-style: solid; border-width: 1.0px 1.0px 1.0px 1.0px; border-color: #ccc; padding: 3.0px 5.0px 3.0px 5.0px; min-width: 70px\"><div>Unlocked Reward</div>",
